item.title: Portforwarding? It hates me
item.dc:creator: @i_hollowfied i_hollowfied
item.description:
@i_hollowfied wrote:

For one you aren’t trying to portforward your no-ip… Your trying to portforward your default gateway so just switch the no-ip to your default gateway and then you connect to 127.0.0.1 then for others set the ip to your no-ip
